      <description>&lt;DIV&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;It has always been our policy that we may post names of those characters before and after getting name changes using the service at our discretion.&amp;nbsp; This is not something we have promised would always be done.&amp;nbsp; Currently with the launch of the new website it was decided not to continue this reporting of changed names, however it can return at any time at our discretion.</description>
